<p n="1-2">
                        Twelfth year of the victorious king Narasiṃhavarman.
                </p>
                
<p n="3-5">
                        Vaṇṇakka Cāttaṉār, the servant 
<supplied reason="subaudible">of</supplied> Pakaimatar, the man 
<supplied reason="explanation">
  <foreign>āḷ</foreign>
</supplied> 
<supplied reason="subaudible">of</supplied> Pācāṟu in Mīkoṉṟaināṭu, fell recapturing cattle.
                </p>
                
